{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e7b5c7df9c","title":"采取围城打援办法歼敌有生力量","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"826d446a41","index":0,"year":1946,"month":10,"day":24,"articleId":"e7b5c7df9c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji4","name":"毛泽东文集第四卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji4.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji4":{"comments":[{"id":"eacacb00b2","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"e7b5c7df9c","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据毛泽东手稿刊印。"},{"id":"f74fbdcefd","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"e7b5c7df9c","index":1,"part_index":1,"offset":3,"text":"詹，指詹才芳，当时任冀东军区司令员。李，指李楚离，一九○六年生，河北元氏人，当时任冀东军区政治委员。王，指王智涛，一九○六年生，河北沧县人，当时任冀东军区参谋长。"},{"id":"4ffbcb6faf","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"e7b5c7df9c","index":2,"part_index":1,"offset":7,"text":"程李，指程子华、李运昌，当时分别任冀热辽军区司令员兼政治委员和副司令员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f4ddf3e5af","type":"title","text":"采取围城打援办法歼敌有生力量","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"e7b5c7df9c"},{"id":"f74fbdcefd","type":"appellation","text":"詹李王并告程李：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"e7b5c7df9c"},{"id":"4ffbcb6faf","type":"paragraph","text":"你们作战方针应着重歼灭敌有生力量，然后敌占各据点自然容易为我收复。为实行此方针，应采取围城打援办法。围城之目的不在得城，而在打援。集中七八倍于敌之兵力（例如集中四五个团打敌援兵一个至二个营），每次事前均应有充分准备，不浪打，打则必胜。打时须用包围迂回，以期尽歼。此点对干部应作深刻教育。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"e7b5c7df9c"},{"id":"69966259e7","type":"paragraph","text":"军 委","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"e7b5c7df9c"},{"id":"a8351fc872","type":"paragraph","text":"酉敬","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"e7b5c7df9c"}],"page":{"id":"173642a32b","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"e7b5c7df9c","start":205,"end":205}}}},"__N_SSG":true}